    <div class="main review-item" id="5012945">
        

  <header class="main-hd">
    <h3 class="title">
      <a href="https://book.douban.com/review/5012945/" class="title-link">一碗含有鱼翅的粉丝</a>
      <div class="toggle_review right">        <a href="javascript:;" id="toggle-5012945"class="indicator unfold j" title="展开全文">        </a>
      </div>
    </h3>
    

<div class="header-more">
    <a class="author-avatar" href="https://www.douban.com/people/4801038/"><img width="48" height="48" src="https://img3.doubanio.com/icon/u4801038-2.jpg"></a>
    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/4801038/" class="author">
      <span property="v:reviewer">树下的Alfred</span>
    </a>    <span property="v:rating" class="allstar30 main-title-rating" title="还行"></span>
  <span property="v:dtreviewed" content="2011-07-05"
      class="main-meta">2011-07-05 23:17:29</span>
</div>

  </header>

        <div class="main-bd">
          <div id="review_5012945_short" class="review-short">
            <div class="short-content">
                  刚开始看这本书的时候，我对于这本书的行文方式和语气非常不满。由于是在厕所里看的，几乎有把书页撕下来当草纸的冲动。而且，为什么这本书以“80后”和“中日混血”、“帅哥”作为卖点！拜托，这又不是男优写真！  在开始的近五十页内，发现这个作者真的是在“讲”故事！文字...

                    <a class="pl" href="https://book.douban.com/review/5012945/#comments">(50回应)</a>
                  <div class="more-info pl clearfix">
                    <span class="left">83有用 / 15没用</span>
                  </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div id="review_5012945_full" class="hidden">
            <div id="review_5012945_full_content" class="full-content"></div>
          </div>
        </div>
    </div>
  </div>

      
  



  <div xmlns:v="http://rdf.data-vocabulary.org/#" typeof="v:Review">
    <div class="main review-item" id="4965394">
        

  <header class="main-hd">
    <h3 class="title">
      <a href="https://book.douban.com/review/4965394/" class="title-link">聊的就是日本</a>
      <div class="toggle_review right">        <a href="javascript:;" id="toggle-4965394"class="indicator unfold j" title="展开全文">        </a>
      </div>
    </h3>
    

<div class="header-more">
    <a class="author-avatar" href="https://www.douban.com/people/wqfengjun/"><img width="48" height="48" src="https://img3.doubanio.com/icon/u36282243-2.jpg"></a>
    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/wqfengjun/" class="author">
      <span property="v:reviewer">风君</span>
    </a>    <span property="v:rating" class="allstar50 main-title-rating" title="力荐"></span>
  <span property="v:dtreviewed" content="2011-05-27"
      class="main-meta">2011-05-27 10:10:35</span>
</div>

  </header>

        <div class="main-bd">
          <div id="review_4965394_short" class="review-short">
            <div class="short-content">
                  关于日本的书，也已经读了不少了，差不多自己也成了一个“日本专家”了。但是当看到这本《当我们聊起日本时》，还是忍不住将其放入书架。原因大致有二：一是本书作者是中日混血，视角或与他人不同；二是作者与我同为“80后”，想来颇有共同语言。  书名称本书“聊日本”，可谓...

                    <a class="pl" href="https://book.douban.com/review/4965394/#comments">(55回应)</a>
                  <div class="more-info pl clearfix">
                    <span class="left">107有用 / 9没用</span>
                  </div>
            </div>
